== Tracking categories ==
* {{clc|Infobox religious building with unknown affiliation}}
* {{clc|Pages using infobox religious building with nrhp}}
* {{clc|Pages using infobox religious building with unsupported parameters}}
* {{clc|No local image but image on Wikidata}} ([https://petscan.wmflabs.org/?language=en&project=wikipedia&categories=No%20local%20image%20but%20image%20on%20Wikidata&ns%5B0%5D=1&templates_yes=Infobox%20religious%20building&search_max_results=500&interface_language=en&active_tab= PetScan list]) – Used by [[Template:Wikidata image]] to track articles where an infobox has no image but [[:en:Wikidata|Wikidata]] has an image name. To exclude articles from this category, add an image or {{para|nocat_wdimage|yes}} to the infobox.

